ass=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T06:03:26.000Z","msg":"實冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"521e8992cd74ccf38eba2bec6f3706f4436dc739","tid":787850,"uid":37651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T06:30:03.000Z","msg":"<strong>5歲臨臨疑被虐殺　生父繼母續還押待死因報告</strong><br />\n<br />\n屯門5歲女童陳瑞臨（臨臨）疑遭虐待致死，其生父及繼母被控1項謀殺罪，案件今在屯門裁判法院再提訊。兩名被告繼續毋須答辯，控方表示死者的死因報告預計將於本月底完成，故申請押後案件，以待控方索取法律意見。裁判官接納控方申請，<span style=\"color: red;\">將案押後至10月16日再提訊</span>，兩名被告均沒有保釋申請，續還押候訊。<br />\n<br />\n兩名被告為臨臨的生父陳海平（26歲），報稱任職運輸工人，以及報稱為家庭主婦的繼母黃曉彤（27歲）被控1項謀殺罪，控罪指兩被告於2018年1月6日，在屯門屯合街2號時代廣場南翼C座謀殺陳瑞臨。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2092357/5%E6%AD%B2%E8%A2%AB%E8%99%90%E8%87%B4%E6%AD%BB%E8%87%A8%E8%87%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%B9%BC%E7%A8%9A%E5%9C%92%E3%80%80%E6%A0%A1%E9%95%B7%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E8%AB%8B%E7%97%85%E5%81%87%E5%B9%BC%E5%9C%92%E6%B7%AA%E7%82%BA%E6%89%98%E5%85%92%E6%89%80?mtc=10016\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2092357%2F5%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%2599%2590%25E8%2587%25B4%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E8%2587%25A8%25E8%2587%25A8%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25B9%25BC%25E7%25A8%259A%25E5%259C%2592%25E3%2580%2580%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E9%2595%25B7%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%259B%25B4%25E8%25AB%258B%25E7%2597%2585%25E5%2581%2587%25E5%25B9%25BC%25E5%259C%2592%25E6%25B7%25AA%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%2589%2598%25E5%2585%2592%25E6%2589%2580%3Fmtc%3D10016&d=AIB9wnxRt8rjcHg3QClxIW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=843e3786\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2092357/5%E6%AD%B2%E8%A2%AB%E8%99%90%E8%87%B4%E6%AD%BB%E8%87%A8%E8%87%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%B9%BC%E7%A8%9A%E5%9C%92%E3%80%80%E6%A0%A1%E9%95%B7%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E8%AB%8B%E7%97%85%E5%81%87%E5%B9%BC%E5%9C%92%E6%B7%AA%E7%82%BA%E6%89%98%E5%85%92%E6%89%80?mtc=10016</a>"},{"pid":"6dbcabafd793dbf39c32c82f3dcfbadb8f50c691","tid":787850,"uid":9286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T06:33:09.000Z","msg